<TEXT>&#2;<DATELINE>2008-12-01</DATELINE><TITLE>Hetero-Diels–Alder reaction of 1,3-bis(trimethylsilyloxy)-1,3-butadienes with arylsulfonylcyanides. Synthesis and antimicrobial activity of 4-hydroxy-2-(arylsulfonyl)pyridines</TITLE><BODY>Abstract Hetero-Diels–Alder reactions of 1,3-bis(silyloxy)-1,3-butadienes with arylsulfonylcyanides afforded a variety of 4-hydroxy-2-(arylsulfonyl)pyridines. Several derivatives show antimicrobial activity against Gram-positive bacteria.&#3;</BODY></TEXT>